title: THE PRINCE & ME 4 - THE ELEPHANT ADVENTURE (2010)
description:
The prince and me 4: Royal adventure in paradise
The Prince & Me: The Elephant Adventure comedy

One year after their royal wedding , King Edvard and Queen Paige , receive an invitation to attend the wedding of the beautiful Princess Myra , daughter of King Sanigkoun . When they arrive in the kingdom, Paige realizes that Mary is miserable. He does not want to marry the scheming and insincere SWR man, chosen for her father , but her beloved mahout , the charming Alou . When revealed the hidden romance , the aluminum goes to jail and the sacred royal elephant disappears into the jungle . The Edvard and Paige could not imagine how this trip would mark the beginning of the greatest adventure of their lives. You can find the lost royal elephant and convince the King that strict Maira should marry for love rather than interest?

    Year of Production: 2010
    duration: 86 minutes
    Directed by : Catherine Cyran
    CREDITS :
